Layout/MultilineMethodCallIndentation.description:
Description

Checks indentation of method calls with the dot operator that span more than one line.
Layout/MultilineMethodCallIndentation.option:
This rule supports the following parameters in your configuration:

EnforcedStyle: aligned (type: str)
SupportedStyles: ['aligned', 'indented', 'indented_relative_to_receiver'] (type: list)
IndentationWidth: None (type: NoneType)
